Today we look at one of the original pioneers in online Minecraft entertainment, who fell from a height of over 12M subscribers after a devastating series of events ranging from a drastic rebrand, to a wave of allegations from former partners and YouTubers. This is the decay of childhood hero SkyDoesMinecraft/NetNobody/Adam Dahlberg.
